<p>Brooklyn Boy</h1></p>

<p>From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</p>


<ref class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</ref>
<ref class="mw-jump-link" href="#p-search">Jump to search</ref>
<p>Brooklyn Boy is a play by American playwright <ref target="/wiki/Donald_Margulies" title="Donald Margulies">Donald Margulies</ref>. The play premiered in 2004 at <ref target="/wiki/South_Coast_Repertory" title="South Coast Repertory">South Coast Repertory</ref> and then on <ref target="/wiki/Broadway_theatre" title="Broadway theatre">Broadway</ref> in 2005.</p>

